\ndiscuss the contribution of Compton-thick AGNs to the rest of the hard X-ray\nbackground.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Aug 2003 14:22:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Sep 2003 09:11:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
